Data Visualizations

Industry Revenues This plot shows the average revenue for each industry. Because the revenues are so varied, they are split up into 6 groups of similar revenue values. Industry Growth This plot shows the average growth for each industry, ordered from least growth to most State Revenues This plot shows the average growth for each industry, ordered from least growth to most State Growth This plot shows the average growth for each industry, ordered from least growth to most Revenue and Growth by City This plot shows the average growth for each industry, ordered from least growth to most Note that the echo = FALSE parameter was added to the code chunk to prevent printing of the R code that generated the plot.
